summary: Check verify-installation prepare plugin
description: |
    Verify that the verify-installation plugin correctly checks
    that packages were installed from expected repositories.
    Tests both successful verification and failure cases.

# TODO: Enable for other provision methods when appropriate
tag+:
  - provision-only
  - provision-container

adjust:
  - when: distro != fedora
    enabled: false
    because: Test uses koji which is Fedora-specific
